name: DataNodeTest

test_cases.name: xmlOutputStyleWithoutCData
test_cases.description: Tests the XML output of a DataNode without CDATA section within a style element.

test_cases.name: xmlOutputOtherWithCData
test_cases.description: Tests the XML output of a DataNode with CDATA section within an 'other' element.

test_cases.name: xmlOutputOtherWithoutCData
